FLANAGAN, Appellant, v. FOX, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. February 5, 1894.) Appeal from city court. Action by James Flanagan, as executor, etc., against Patrick Fox.

Argued before BOOKSTAVER, BISCHOFF, and PRYOR, JJ.

No opinion. Motion for leave to appeal to the court of appeals granted. See 26 N. Y. Supp. 48.
